edu.jhu.cs.oose.fall2011.cartagena.iface
Class CartagenaMoveEvent

java.lang.Object
  edu.jhu.cs.oose.fall2011.cartagena.iface.CartagenaMoveEvent

public class CartagenaMoveEvent
extends java.lang.Object

Represents an event in which a Cartagena player has made a move, thus changing the Cartagena model. These events should be dispatched to all listeners when any move is made in the Cartagena model.
